OL,3,CExplicit photo reportedly shared with
OL,4,Cchildren in world record attempt
OL,6,FA sexually explicit photo has
OL,7,Freportedly been shared with minors as
OL,8,Fpart of a world record attempt.
OL,10,FAn email from Jersey College
OL,11,FPreparatory School to parents, and
OL,12,Fseen by ITV News, states that "a large
OL,13,Fgroup of children across the island,
OL,14,Fincluding primary-age children, have
OL,15,Fbeen added to a WhatsApp group where
OL,16,Fthe original intention was to break
OL,17,Fthe Guinness World Record for the
OL,18,Flargest WhatsApp group".
