OL,6,FThe email explains that since then, an
OL,7,Findividual has reportedly posted a
OL,8,Fsexually explicit picture in the group.
OL,10,FDeputy Headteacher Nadia Guglieri adds
OL,11,Fthat police are aware of the incident
OL,12,Fand this is being sent out as a
OL,13,Fwarning for parents to be vigilant, as
OL,14,Fthey "have not received any reports of
OL,15,Fany children from our school being
OL,16,Faffected".
