OL,6,FUnder WhatsApp's terms and conditions,
OL,7,Fusers must be at least 13 years old to
OL,8,Fhave an account, but Ms Guglieri
OL,9,Fstresses that "some younger children
OL,10,Fdo have access to phones and may be
OL,11,Fadded to group chats without fully
OL,12,Funderstanding the risks".
OL,14,FShe asks parents to regularly check
OL,15,Ftheir child's phone activity and to
OL,16,F"stay curious about any groups they
OL,17,Fmay have joined".
