OL,6,FMs Guglieri adds: "It's also important
OL,7,Fto be aware that WhatsApp settings
OL,8,Foften allow images shared in groups to
OL,9,Fbe automatically saved to the device's
OL,10,Fcamera roll."
OL,12,FThe maximum group size for the popular
OL,13,Fmessaging app is 1,024 members.
OL,15,FAny parent who believes their child
OL,16,Fmay have been exposed to sexually
OL,17,Fexplicit content is asked to contact
OL,18,Fthe States of Jersey Police on 01534
OL,19,F612612.
